,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-034-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Wait……為什麼突然講到我的生日啊。\n我不是都說今天主角是你嗎","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-034-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"是的，所以才更要那麼說！　今天大家很用心\n幫我慶祝生日，PAREO真的覺得自己非常幸福","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-034-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"所以，大家生日的時候，\n我也想讓大家體會PAREO今天所感受到的幸福\n到時候我會滿懷著感謝的心回報大家！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-034-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"……你想怎麼做就怎麼做吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-034-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"是的～！　請讓我照著自己的意思去做♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-034-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"你要是閒著就去聽音樂吧。\n去試試剛才我拿給你的耳機吧？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-034-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"咦！　要用和CHU²大人成對的那個耳機嗎？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-034-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Yes。不過，成對的部分不只有外觀。\n品質也和我那隻耳機相同，我是用最高規格訂製的。\n我也有幫你事先暖好機了","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-034-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplayName":"PAREO","body":"居居居然！　連規格也和CHU²大人的耳機一樣！\n那可一定要放進要上鎖的玻璃展示櫃裡了……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":34,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":34,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-034-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"真是的，你搞錯重點了！\n雖然東西都已經送出去了，還管東管西的也很奇怪……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"angry02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-034-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"我都特地訂製了能讓你充分享受音樂的最高規格，\n但你居然要把他拿來供著，這樣完全就是Nonsense！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"angry02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"2021birthdayMemorial-034-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":34}],"windowDisplay